---
title: Enchilada-Glazed Pork Meatballs with Garlic-Spinach Rice & Charred Corn Salsa
description: No other sauce is fit to do such a job that the enchilada sauce does — glazing pork meatballs so that they become irresistible.
That’s why it’s the ruler of this dish. The sauce is mopped up by a spinach rice and charred corn salsa to add that much-loved smokey
sweet flavour.

